{"tid":1977194,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"好多藍店就黎頂唔住","createTime":"2020-04-17T19:02:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-17T20:07:14.000Z","uid":91897,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"408b3b9e4d0c735791da242d2f33e5fc1823abab","tid":1977194,"uid":91897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T19:02:38.000Z","msg":"你地呢班藍絲有咩資格同人講自己係藍架？<br />\n<br />\n根本你地就係偽藍，咁多藍店就黎頭唔順都唔出黎支持？<br />\n遲d 政府派錢要捐比佢地幫補下，香港無左佢地真係唔得，如果得番d 黃店 的話你叫大家點食得安樂<br />\n<br />\nPs: 請只支持高調支持警察的店，特別是楊明的燉 和西九龍空姐牛肉飯 ，不用支持其他所謂的藍店，因為佢地分分鐘係假惺惺作態，除非佢地高調表明立場支持警察，否則不會幫襯"},{"pid":"c9d632cf6acd12841d9ea78435e34453ffb58725","tid":1977194,"uid":160592,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T19:13:07.000Z","msg":"藍店醒好多<br />\n至小唔會見到空姐鬧銀龍"},{"pid":"36dd8321f7639e3cd807eed5df84972f054a4ea6","tid":1977194,"uid":189109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T19:23:28.000Z","msg":"冇捐過錢畀藍店唔好話自己係藍<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c812735d65632230f13aabdc148d07d8e0db945","tid":1977194,"uid":286897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T19:39:13.000Z","msg":"*你*你老母臭*返鋪頭喺度放屁又彈玩政治懶擦你哋班男 藍色商戶 <br />\n乜都冇做過<br />\n淨係淨係出去chen就算唔係嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你對唔對得住啲警察<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後支持警察吞槍自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\"